A way to increase patient trust in doctors for medical staff in order to increase the health metrics in patients.
A way to decrease burnout for doctors with high patient loads to increase retention time for doctors in high stress job positions. 
A way to support the long term care of patients for nursing and medical staff to rapidly familiarize medical staff with patient medical and personal history to increase quality of care.
A way to comfort patients for medical staff to increase patient post-care surveys.
A way to foster a connection between doctors and patients for medical staff to increase health metrics in patients.
